    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. While the engine and transmission are mechanically sound and have been serviced regularly, the car shows clear signs of its age and mileage. You will find some noticeable scratches and minor dings on the exterior paint, and the interior upholstery exhibits moderate wear and tear. It is a solid, functional vehicle that runs well, though it is not in showroom condition and may require some routine maintenance typical for a car of this era.",
      "price": 18500.0,
