    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior has several noticeable dents, rusting on the door panels, and the paint is heavily faded. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and there is a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips intermittently; a full inspection and major repairs are highly recommended before any long-distance driving.",
      "price": 8500.0,
